    id: "og-amedex-0104",
    topic: "Obstetrics & Gynaecology",
    subtopic: "Fetal valproate syndrome",
    stem: `Which of the following medications, if taken during pregnancy, could have caused the facial anomalies shown in the following photograph?`,
