    topic: "Obstetrics & Gynaecology",
    subtopic: "Placental abruption",
    stem: `A 32-year-old woman presents to the emergency department with vaginal bleeding at 28 weeks of pregnancy. After prompt investigations, placental abruption is diagnosed. Which of the following options is not expected to be caused by the condition?`,
