    stem: `A 34-year-old pregnant woman presents at 32 weeks of pregnancy for an antenatal visit. On pelvic examination, breech presentation is suspected. Ultrasound shows that fetal hips are flexed, and the knees extended. Which one of the following is this presentation called?`,
