    subtopic: "Gestational diabetes follow-up",
    stem: `A 27-year-old woman, diagnosed with gestational diabetes at 28 weeks of pregnancy, has been being managed at a high-risk pregnancy clinic until 38 weeks when she vaginally delivered a healthy 4-kg baby without any complications. Which one of the following is correct regarding follow-up?`,
