    topic: "Obstetrics & Gynaecology",
    subtopic: "Varicella Zoster in Pregnancy",
    stem: `Martha, 42 years of age, has developed a rash characteristic of chickenpox today, just five days before her expected date of delivery. She is 37 weeks pregnant. Which one of the following is the most appropriate management to prevent neonatal chickenpox?`,
