    topic: "Obstetrics & Gynaecology",
    subtopic: "DVT management in pregnancy",
    stem: `A 32-year-old woman is diagnosed with deep vein thrombosis (DVT) of the iliofemoral vein at 18 weeks gestation. Which one of the following is the next best step in management?`,
